<subSubSection id="C37642ECFFCBFFFFFD735AC95924FCEB" pageId="38" pageNumber="590" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFCBFFFFFD735AC95924FCEB" blockId="38.[718,1312,586,1013]" pageId="38" pageNumber="590">
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFCBFFFFFD735AC959FDFD75" authorityName="Bangs" authorityYear="1901" box="[719,924,704,737]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Diplomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="38" pageNumber="590" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="labilis">Diplomys labilis</taxonomicName>
has been variously placed in the genera 
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFCBFFFFFC2B5AE2599FFC9C" authorityName="G. Cuvier" authorityYear="1809" box="[919,1022,747,776]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Echimys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="38" pageNumber="590" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Echimys</taxonomicName>
or 
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFCBFFFFFB935AE25ECAFC9C" authorityName="Lund" authorityYear="1839" box="[1071,1195,747,776]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Phyllomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="38" pageNumber="590" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Phyllomys</taxonomicName>
by early authors; O. Thomas in 1916 was the first to assign it to 
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFCBFFFFFC315B3F5E63FCC3" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" box="[909,1026,822,855]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Diplomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="38" pageNumber="590" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Diplomys</taxonomicName>
. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption id="DF1341EFFFCBFFFFFD6C5B8C5988FBD1" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6623830" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6623830" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6623830/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="590" startId="38.[108,132,1020,1053]" targetBox="[107,696,595,1007]" targetPageId="38">
<subSubSection id="C37642ECFFCBFFFFFD6C5B8C5E53FC61" pageId="38" pageNumber="590" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFCBFFFFFD6C5B8C5E01FC32" blockId="38.[718,1312,586,1013]" box="[720,1120,901,934]" pageId="38" pageNumber="590">
<emphasis id="B918CD75FFCBFFFFFD6C5B8C5E01FC32" bold="true" box="[720,1120,901,934]" pageId="38" pageNumber="590">Subspecies and Distribution.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFCBFFFFFD6C5BAD5E53FC61" blockId="38.[718,1312,586,1013]" pageId="38" pageNumber="590">
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFCBFFFFFD6C5BAD5E45FC5A" authority="Bangs, 1901" authorityName="Bangs" authorityYear="1901" box="[720,1060,932,974]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Diplomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="38" pageNumber="590" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="labilis">D. I. labilis Bangs, 1901</taxonomicName>
